  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this observational study is to further evaluate the safety and performance of
      the EnligHTN™ Renal Denervation System in the treatment of patients with uncontrolled
      hypertension in clinical routine practice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The EnligHTN European Observational study is designed to collect more data, critical to the
      benefit of the therapy, within a clinical routine setting.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
